text: Zhu Zhengjun (born 16 November 1971) is a Chinese former cyclist. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of China Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in cycling Category:Asian Games silver medalists for China Category:Cyclists at the 1994 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 1994 Asian Games
